comments: Dr. Acosta is a nice person. With that said: She grades lesson plans hard and does not follow the rubric. Be very careful and ask lots of questions when she goes over the rubric. Write down what she wants and stick to what she says not the rubric. She takes off points for not using a paper clip. She does grade easy on all other assignments.
